tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'Semantic Search', detail: 'Search knowledge base for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('Semantic Search')
const result = await agent(
  `Execute the semantic search workflow defined in workflows/semantic-search.md for the following query.

Working directory: /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

Query: "DBからデータを読み込んで集計し、結果を別テーブルに書き込む定期処理を作りたい。どういう構成で実装すればいい？（処理方式: Nablarchバッチ）（目的: 実装したい）"

Read the file workflows/semantic-search.md and follow it exactly. Return the selected_sections array as JSON with fields: file, section_id, relevance (high/partial), reason. Also return selected_pages and excluded_pages arrays.

For each page record why it was selected or skipped.
For each section record why it was selected (high/partial) or skipped.

Return a JSON object with:
- selected_pages: array of {path, reason}
- excluded_pages: array of {path, reason} 
- selected_sections: array of {file, section_id, relevance, reason}
- excluded_sections: array of {file, section_id, reason}`,
  {
    schema: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        selected_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        selected_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
          }
        }
      },
      required: ['selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'selected_sections', 'excluded_sections']
    }
  }
)

return result
